Text: POWERSHARES FTSE RAFI US 1500 SMALL-MID PORTFOLIO (BMV:PRFZ) Declares  -  Dividend of $0.37 POWERSHARES FTSE RAFI US 1500 SMALL-MID PORTFOLIO (BMV:PRFZ) announced a  -  dividend on Monday, September 23rd, Wall Street Journal reports.
